{{Top|leg}}
Brightly-lit '''marquee droids''' were used in public areas by businesses and other organizations to advertise their locations or draw the attention of a passerby to something in the immediate area. The [[Droid/Legends|droids]] were equipped with [[Repulsorlift/Legends|repulsorlifts]] so that they and their messages could draw as much attention as possible. Depending on where they were ordered to go, they could stay in a single position, float around within a specified area, or follow a specified object or person.

